{"title":"乡里同事","authors":["侗肄"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":5,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡里同事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侗肄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邮递员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色邮包里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂号寄出一条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵肠挂肚的乡路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月、青春、爱情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默读远方的回音壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句人生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如读双鬓飞雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驻乡民警"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枚橄榄绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩映了一方乡景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路爱民拳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"招式走十里祥和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗定心丸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡情口碑成美谈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地管理员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守一寸土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如守一只婴儿奶瓶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如灾年守一碗干饭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尺寸量成誓词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人情由此变短"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为“福建省”的“失守”［注］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"良心也捏出了泪滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首的“雄鸡图案”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该是祖先和未来的深沉写意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：据统计，建国以来我国的耕地已减少了一个福建省的面积。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}